name: Katie Greene
text: Love Nick & Willys.  Port Washington Location was my first and they are amazing, amazing people.  Moved to Kenosha and had a great experience at this location.  My husband let us get a pizza with veggies and he enjoyed it! Thank you!  I love the ingredients & customer service!

name: Bo Boone
text: Nice staff, good pizza and reasonable price. We enjoyed the visit.

name: Chris Mostoller
text: Pizza is different from the usual chain pizza restaurants.... Not bad, but not great.
